ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v281.group

Class OMP_O09_PATIENT_VISIT

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractStructure
      • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractGroup
        • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v281.group.OMP_O09_PATIENT_VISIT
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Group, Structure, Visitable, Serializable

    public class OMP_O09_PATIENT_VISIT
extends AbstractGroup

    Represents a OMP_O09_PATIENT_VISIT group structure (a Group object). A Group is an ordered collection of message segments that can repeat together or be optionally in/excluded together. This Group contains the following elements:

    • 1: PV1 (Patient Visit)
    • 2: PV2 (Patient Visit - Additional Information) optional
    • 3: PRT (Participation Information) optional repeating
    • 4: ARV (Access Restriction) optional repeating
